<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Synopsys cut, stock sinks.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Synopsys cut, stock sinks.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- SoundView analyst Erach Desai cut his long-term rating of Synopsys Inc to hold from buy on Thursday. His short-term rating of the company remains hold.</p>
<p>-- Desai left 1997 earnings estimated unchanged at $1.45 a share but cut 1998 profit estimates to $1.80 from $1.90 a share.</p>
<p>--- Shares closed down 3-5/16 to 24-3/8.</p>
